body:
Should this work with autotest.sh?
If I comment assign out then it works. It seems iverilog simulates code between translate_off/on.

```
module z_test( in, en, out);
  input [7:0] in;
  input en;
  inout [7:0] out;

//  assign out = en ? in : 8'bx;

  // synopsys translate_off

  assign out = 8'b10101010;

  // synopsys translate_on

endmodule

```

